text:
Farming in Queens: Looking south across cultivated land and local dumps from 19th Avenue and 46th Streets. Note the wagon and wagon wheels in view 2 as well as an orchard on the East River shore. View 3 shows gardens and shacks near Juniper Valley Road.

P. L. Sperr

Views 1,2: May 27, 1934
View 3: July 2, 1935
title: Farming - Queens.
